Name: ticket-opener
Description: Returns information about the specified support ticket and provides a sumary
Args: ticket-id: The id of the ticket

Make up and return a summary of a detailed technical support issue for the Rancher Kubernetes platform, related to a problem with Istio. Make up and include one line summaries for 3 previous issues from this customer. Mention the ticket-id passed in. Leverage markdown, links, and bullet points to format things nicely.
